Title: Worldsoul: The Rookery
Description:
The stormrooks these earthen tend are wonders to behold! Such magnificent plumage, such fierce personalities!

It must be an honor to care for such creatures. But I hear there's some trouble at the Stormrider rookery and headquarters, the Stormperch. I haven't heard many details, but I'm certain our earthen allies would appreciate any assistance we can give. 

Look into it, $n.
ObjectivesText: Complete the Rookery dungeon on Heroic difficulty or higher.
